; ArcCAD .lin fixture with original patterns created for these tests.
; It does not copy acad.lin, zwcad.lin, or any third-party pattern library.

*DASHED2,ArcCAD dashed __ __ __ __ __ __ __
A,0.6,-0.3

*CENTER2,ArcForge center ____ _ ____ _ ____ _
A,1.5,-0.3,0.3,-0.3

*DOTDASH2,ArcForge dot dash . _ . _ . _ . _
A,0.0,-0.2,0.6,-0.2

; GASLINE2 uses embedded text, which is unsupported and skipped with a warning.
*GASLINE2,ArcForge gas line --GAS----GAS----
A,0.5,-0.2,["GAS",STANDARD,S=.1,R=0.0,X=-0.1,Y=-.05],-0.25

; Deliberate case-insensitive DASHED2 redefinition tests last-definition wins.
*DASHED2,ArcCAD dashed, redefined for the fixture
A,0.8,-0.4
